snippet: Skal Labissiere scored 26 points, Isaiah Briscoe had 11 points and 12 rebounds, and No. 2 Kentucky ran away from visiting New Jersey Institute of Technology, 87-57.
abstract: Kentucky defeats New Jersey Institute of Technology, 87-57, in college basketball; other results noted.
